g levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Easy levels - that are easy...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reverse realm - Beat the levels... upside down!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jump King - Get to the top</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gravity-man - Use gravity changers to win</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are many traps in the game, such as spikes, toxic water, shooting walls, black matter, etc. The enemies have several variations. from small fast opponents to big bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy a journey of The Pit Warrior, use ladders, teleporters or even gravity changers and save the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Here we go!</p>","developers":["Creative Seal"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2480850/header.jpg?t=1736720265","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257075491,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257075491/movie480.mp4?t=1732189852","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257075491/movie_max.mp4?t=1732189852"},"name":"The Pit Arcade Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257075491/adc6ce9ec99f0309bfec31bea030fa8b24b0af31/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1732189852","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257075491/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1732189852","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257075491/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1732189852"}}],"name":"The Pit Arcade","package_groups":[{"description":"","display_type":0,"is_recurring_subscription":"false","name":"default","save_text":"","selection_text":"Select a purchase option","subs":[{"can_get_free_license":"0","is_free_license":false,"option_description":"","option_text":"The Pit Arcade - $7.99 USD","packageid":8928